—ظSarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/is-terminal.mdظ@9b9073a78d50b641ec42d2d7055577c8aa3d066178b636a981f17f7b74cfdcaf²title: is-terminal‘¨ExamplesظفReturn "terminal attached" if standard input is attached to a terminal, and "no terminal" if not.
